{"commands": [{"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "\n%md-sandbox\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 0; padding-top: 9px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://databricks.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/db-academy-rgb-1200px.png\" alt=\"Databricks Learning\" style=\"width: 1200px\">\n</div>", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "0056a680-f391-4aae-aa57-cd72e5669d0d", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "8665a2f4-f63a-4e69-a616-5f254d03414e", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 1, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md-sandbox\n<img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/Apache-Spark-Logo_TM_200px.png\" style=\"float: left: margin: 20px\"/>\n\n# Gold Layer - Real-time Clickstream analysis\n\nIn this exercise you will need to implement a real-time rolling window to see how many clicks we receive on our website every 5 minutes.\n\n## In this exercise you will:\n* Learn how to set Spark shuffle partitions\n* Practice using `window` in Structured Streaming\n\n## Prerequisites\n* Web browser: **Chrome**\n* A cluster configured with **8 cores** and **DBR 7.0**", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "3afa93ea-b47d-41d8-bb42-475d3dd10aec", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "a2c7960b-a53d-4ca5-958a-0bee7581ae62", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 2, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md-sandbox\n<h2 style=\"color:red\">Instructor Note</h2>\n\n\n\nThings to talk about:\n- talk about the goal: we'd like to monitor the incoming click live but also smoothened by collecting the data in a 5 min window\n- describe the basic streaming concepts in spark if the audience is not familiar with them. For this purpose you can use the latest version of the [Structured Streaming courseware](https://files.training.databricks.com/courses/ilt/#Structured-Streaming-lnk) or the [Spark tutorial](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/structured-streaming-programming-guide.html#programming-model) on this topic. Do not go into too much detail though, a basic understanding of the streaming concepts and how the streamreader should be used is sufficient.\n- show the streaming tab on Spark UI introduced in 3.0\n- why shuffle partition is important and how it is changed in Spark 3.0 with [Adaptive Query Execution](https://databricks.com/blog/2020/05/29/adaptive-query-execution-speeding-up-spark-sql-at-runtime.html) (note that AQE is not available with streaming queries in 3.0)\n- reiterate on window() function and how can they access the beginning of the window ", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "ef79d19b-c161-43a1-aa09-df7f40a6605c", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "71e0aba8-245b-4c72-959c-e28cb022baa1", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 3, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Classroom-Setup<br>\n\nFor each lesson to execute correctly, please make sure to run the **`Classroom-Setup`** cell at the start of each lesson (see the next cell) and the **`Classroom-Cleanup`** cell at the end of each lesson.", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "8d132cb9-36cd-4f70-8796-eaa1441cd009", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "7e7aa644-84f4-4ef1-b6f5-a4d814491edd", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 4, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%run ./Includes/PCF-19G-ClassroomSetup", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "9f9e7514-23ac-456e-a73c-b3c564d76551", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "eafba077-ae0d-44d2-8643-a400c14f8886", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 5, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Steps to complete<br>\nImplement the **`challenge()`** function to achieve the following:\n- Set **`spark.sql.shuffle.partitions`** to 8.\n- Set up a file based streaming datasource with Structured Streaming.\n- Implement a rolling 5-minute window (with a 5 second slide interval) and count the number of clicks in every window.\n- Create a DataFrame with the **`window.start`** and **`click_count`** columns and visualize the results.\n\nThe expected Streaming DataFrame schema has to look like this:\n\n|name|type|\n|---|---|\n|ts|TimestampType|\n|click_count|LongType|", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "338342f0-2787-4053-a9b9-055248a12610", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "d6a7e41b-9158-4a58-94e5-ba1726eebb12", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 6, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n#### ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Our streaming folder contains a set of JSON files: ", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "c8070af5-17c3-4325-a07f-8fd539ea9c87", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "13edc7d1-b91d-4927-b0bb-d5548dd7fa2c", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 7, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "display(dbutils.fs.ls(clickstreamFolder))", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "2039383d-e0b0-41f8-8eba-e9b92e8963f4", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "6db31ed3-3cb3-41f0-a699-ff9196547eac", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 8, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "// ANSWER\n\ndef solution(spark:org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession, clickstreamFolder:String, clickstreamSchema:org.apache.spark.sql.types.StructType) : DataFrame = {\n  import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._\n  \n  // Set Spark SQL Shuffle Partitions to 8.\n  spark.conf.set(\"spark.sql.shuffle.partitions\", 8)\n  \n  // Create a Streaming DataFrame, which reads the file from the streaming_folder.\n  // Use the `clickstreamSchema` provided above.\n  // Make sure only a single file is read per trigger.\n  val salesStream = (spark.readStream.schema(clickstreamSchema).format(\"json\")\n                  .option(\"path\",clickstreamFolder)\n                  .option(\"maxFilesPerTrigger\",1)\n                  .load())\n  \n  // Convert `order_timestamp` from unix timestamp to datetime. \n  // Make sure that the unix timestamp has 3 extra zeroes at the end.\n  // Count the number of clicks by record.\n  // Filter for valid timestamps only (remove nulls).\n  val cnts = (salesStream\n          .select(from_unixtime(col(\"order_timestamp\")/1000).alias(\"ts\"), size(col(\"clicked_items\")).alias(\"click_count\"))\n          .filter(col(\"ts\").isNotNull===true))\n  \n  // Create a rolling window with a window interval of 5 minutes,\n  // and a slide interval of 5 seconds. Sum up the click counts.\n  val g = cnts.groupBy(window(cnts.col(\"ts\"),\"5 minutes\",\"5 seconds\")).sum(\"click_count\")\n\n  // Keep two columns only: \n  // 1. the window's start time as `ts`and\n  // 2. the total click count as `click_count`.\n  val twoColsDF = g.select(col(\"window.start\").alias(\"ts\"), col(\"sum(click_count)\").alias(\"click_count\"))\n          \n  // Order by `ts` and return the resulting DataFrame.\n  twoColsDF.orderBy(\"ts\")\n}\n\nval finalDF = solution(spark, clickstreamFolder, clickstreamSchema)\n\n// After displaying finalDF, create a line chart of clicks.\ndisplay(finalDF)", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "26537824-1202-4191-b9f8-7dcd751c6e07", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "deebf485-5dba-4b86-8e4f-2c5a09ae14e4", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 9, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n<h2><img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png\"> Reality Check</h2>\n\nRun the following cell to make sure you are on track:", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "bf6da3a3-6c33-486b-b127-57baabfa8d02", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "b266f0a3-2998-409d-957c-d40b316aad5e", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 10, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "// ANSWER - Test your solution\nrealityCheck(solution, spark, clickstreamFolder, clickstreamSchema)", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "84585770-af29-457b-b786-cf7823eee69b", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "925602a4-27d7-4cc6-8e49-11fe21ba4823", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 11, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Classroom-Cleanup<br>\n\nRun the **`Classroom-Cleanup`** cell below to remove any artifacts created by this lesson.", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "3bc2f87b-bfd7-491f-bd1d-459010befdb3", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "12fe930b-6e8f-4bc7-8c29-a2de05dbc5ef", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 12, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%run ./Includes/Classroom-Cleanup\n", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "e5232fbf-78db-4376-a57c-e143578ef0c7", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "0580d9fb-5aed-4d0f-952d-253ca688bbb3", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 13, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md-sandbox\n&copy; 2020 Databricks, Inc. A